title: HAPPY ELEPHANT
description: In this cute animal makeover game you have to take care of a little elephant. Help it pick coconuts from a tree and clean it after an unvoluntary bath in the mud hole. After so much excitement, the adorable jumbo really deserves a tasty coconut drink. Then it's time to show your styling skills: dress up the cute creature and put together an outfit you like best. Look how happy the sweet elephant is!
